\pard\plain \tx1123\tx1685\tx2246\tx2794\tx3355\tx3917\tx4478\tx5040\tx5602\tx6163\tx6725\fi720\ri-720\sl288\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 And Hill?}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Hill had his plump pinky finger stuck halfway up his own nose, digging for gold.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Leave some for me,\u8221\'94 Mandri joked.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Hill 's eyes flashed, and his rough cheeks screwed up. He gave Mandri a pulled punch in the ribs. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m sick of this shit,\u8221\'94 Hill said. \u8220\'93Take the little dent to the pit.\u8221\'94 He marched past both Mandri and Seb, taking his torchlight with him, disappearing into a sidelong passage.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Gutwipe,\u8221\'94 Seb muttered.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Mandri wondered how they were supposed to carry on without any light.}}